&quot;HARRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRR!&quot; he howled.

Meanwhile...

As Perseus takes his first step down the stairs, he hears the door being smashed, followed by a blood-curdling howl. 

&quot;Make sure Elita is out of harm&#39;s way.  I believe that our prisoner who murdered those policemen earlier, is back on the loose,&quot; said Perseus with a sigh. &quot;He seems to have a perverse fascination with killing....&quot; 

&quot;Hey dinosaur bones!  Wasn&#39;t this guy with you Predacons?&quot; said Ravenchief with a slightly juvenile, but nevertheless accusatory tone.

Meanwhile...

 Salveo jumps over the the security system and sees the broken cell bars and broken glass around Trelos&#39; cell.

&quot;That crazy dog-bot is on the loose again!&quot; he said to Guardia. 

&quot;Damn...&quot; exclaimed Guardia, pulling out her shield and pistol, then runing out the door and dowstairs where everyone else is. 

